    "description": {
      "content": "The Debbie Platform API is a RESTful interface for debt-collection operations on the Debbie SaaS platform. It exposes resources for creditors, cases, customers (debtors), payments and payouts, vouchers, files, updates, and webhook subscriptions.\n\nContact Support:\n Name: Debbie API Support\n Email: api-support@debbie.dk",
